answers.body_markdown:
You don&#39;t need to specify any custom maven configuration to address your need.&lt;br&gt;

In `src/main/resources`, simply create  a `META-INF` folder and place your files here.&lt;br&gt;
In this way, you could find them in the `META-INF` folder of the built JAR. &lt;br&gt;

Besides, you should remove the  `&lt;resource&gt;` element you added in the `pom.xml` since it changes the default resource folder to the root of the project instead of the default `src/main/resources`.

    
If you want to add files and a directory to the META-INF folder use this code in your pom.xml

       &lt;build&gt;
    		&lt;finalName&gt;CustomJsfComponents&lt;/finalName&gt;
    		&lt;resources&gt;
    			&lt;resource&gt;
    				&lt;directory&gt;src/main/resources&lt;/directory&gt;
    				&lt;includes&gt;
    					&lt;include&gt;**.xml&lt;/include&gt;
    					&lt;include&gt;**resources/**&lt;/include&gt;
    				&lt;/includes&gt;
    				&lt;targetPath&gt;META-INF&lt;/targetPath&gt;
    			&lt;/resource&gt;
    		&lt;/resources&gt;
    	&lt;/build&gt;

Modify your pom by adding **webResources**

    &lt;plugin&gt;
                &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;
                &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-war-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;
                &lt;version&gt;2.3&lt;/version&gt;
                &lt;configuration&gt;
                    &lt;failOnMissingWebXml&gt;false&lt;/failOnMissingWebXml&gt;
                    &lt;webResources&gt;
                        &lt;resource&gt;
                            &lt;directory&gt;target/classes/META-INF/&lt;/directory&gt;
                            &lt;includes&gt;
                                &lt;include&gt;*.*&lt;/include&gt;
                            &lt;/includes&gt;
                            &lt;targetPath&gt;META-INF/&lt;/targetPath&gt;
                        &lt;/resource&gt;
                    &lt;/webResources&gt;
                &lt;/configuration&gt;
            &lt;/plugin&gt;

Consider the config.properties file to be found in 

    src / main / resources / META-INF / config.properties


